1-turn off your car
2- get out of the car
3- open the trunk 
4 -look for the spare tire, the jack and the wrench 
5- Use the kac to uplift the car
6-use the wrench to remove the lug nuts from the flat tire
7-remove flat tire
8-put the spare tire instead of the flat tire
9-put back the lug nuts
10-lower the jack
11-put the tools and the flat tire in the trunk 
12- close the trunk
13-get back in the car 
14-drive safe!
